---
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
    <h2 class="text-[32px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-[40px]">
      20 de minute.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-1 text-[32px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-300 sm:text-[40px]">
      De la cutie la prima vanzare.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-8">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="text-[72px] font-light leading-none text-primary-100 md:text-[96px]" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <div class="mt-[-12px] relative">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-neutral-900">Instalezi de pe USB</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
            Stick USB bootabil. Pornesti PC-ul, astepti 15 minute. Linux + Tapselo, gata. Orice PC vechi merge.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="text-[72px] font-light leading-none text-primary-100 md:text-[96px]" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <div class="mt-[-12px] relative">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-neutral-900">Activezi cu un cod</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
            6 caractere din panoul admin. Il tastezi pe terminal, dispozitivul e activ. Fara tehnicieni.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="text-[72px] font-light leading-none text-primary-100 md:text-[96px]" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <div class="mt-[-12px] relative">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold text-neutral-900">Vinzi</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
            Scanezi, incasezi, tiparesti bon fiscal. Cu sau fara internet — sync automat in cloud.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
